formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.	Amount reported in sr. no. 7 is actual amount received from customers towards booking advance but excludes all taxes imposed on sale of flat.   
2.	In the absence of specific guideline regarding interest on capital paid by firm to partners, it was included in estimated as well cost incurred and paid at time of applying for registration and thereafter in quarterly compliance made under RERA up to 31/03/2019.However after issue of Guidance Note-1 dated 09/07/02019 in which it is clearly mentioned as While certifying cost  incurred & paid for the project , interest on partners capital must not be considered as it is own capital and not borrowed fund. This is in accordance with Technical Guidance  for Certifications & Audit under real Estate (Regulation & Development)Act, 2016 issued by ICAI we have reduced the interest cost on partners capital from the cost incurred and paid.
3.	We are unable to certify the detail of PAN no and Mobile number of the customer, since the necessary evidence is not in the possession of the firm.
